Hazariel is one of thirteen [[solar]]s of the [[Panopticon]] of [[Daanvi]], charged with overseeing the [[plane]] of [[Syrania]]. He is called upon to cast down [[radiant idol]]s, exiling them to the [[Material Plane|Eberron]].